    "description": "Complete collection for all E-Commerce API endpoints.\n\n**Authentication:** Write endpoints require `X-API-Key` header. GET /api/products/** is public.\n\nRun the folders in order: Products → Orders → Error Cases.\nProduct and order IDs are captured automatically via test scripts.",
